{
  "texts": [
    "Firstly, group signatures and ring signatures offer significant advantages in protecting the privacy of group members.",
    "They allow group members to remain anonymous when signing documents while ensuring the validity of the signature.",
    "This technology plays a crucial role in scenarios such as internal corporate decision-making and online voting.",
    "Ring signatures find widespread use in blockchain applications, ensuring transaction anonymity and traceability.",
    "Blind signature technology has unique advantages in information transmission and authentication."
  ]
}